snippet.title: Starsiege: Deadzone - 7 Minutes of Alpha Gameplay
snippet.description:
An early look of Alpha gameplay from Starsiege: Deadzone. This video covers 7 minutes of multiplayer gameplay that takes place on an abandoned ship in the Kuiper Belt.

Request access on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2170420/Starsiege_Deadzone/
Follow our Twitter for updates: https://twitter.com/PlayDEADZONE
Join the Discord: discord.gg/7Ewbt6f7MP
